<template>
  <router-view />
</template>

<script>
import HelloWorld from "./components/HelloWorld";
import LoadingScreen from "./components/LoadingScreen";

export default {
  name: "App",
  components: {
    HelloWorld,
    LoadingScreen,
  },
  data() {
    return { isLoading: true };
  },
  mounted() {
    setTimeout(() => {
      this.isLoading = false;
    }, 3000);
  },
};
</script>
